<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WCloud - Emulador de Windows</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #4A90E2, #145DA0);
            color: white;
            padding: 50px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
        .btn {
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #145DA0;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #ddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Bem-vindo ao WCloud</h1>
    <p>Emule seu Windows e jogue à vontade!</p>
    <a href="#" class="btn">Iniciar Emulação</a>
</body>
</html>
